    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini dei eterni, anno incarnationis eius millesimo centesimo
                        quinquagesimo VI, octavo idus iunii, indictione IIII. Manifesti sumus nos,
                            <persName ref="#people/3215">Passavantus</persName> filius quondam
                            <persName ref="#people/3216">Sesmundini</persName> cum uxore mea
                            <persName ref="#people/3225">Berta</persName>, undecim libras bonorum
                        denariorum mutuo accepissemus a domno <persName><name ref="Wido"
                                >Uuidone</name></persName>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Hospitals"><rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >ospitali</rs>
                            <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Hospitals"
                            >Altipasti</placeName></orgName> rectore. Pro quibus, per hanc cartulam
                        pignoris nomine damus et concedimus in ipso ospitali suisque rectoribus
                        habere, tenere, laborare, husufructuando in donicato, videlicet integram
                        ipsam nostram petiam terre positam <placeName ref="#places/3210">in
                            Pratale</placeName>, et <rs key="#Seigneurial_district">curte</rs>
                        nostra de <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Wine #Seigneurial_district"
                            >Puzzo</placeName> prope <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs> que vocatur
                        Pactronise. De alia via sibi currit. De aliis partibus <persName
                            ref="#people/3226">Castracani</persName> et de consortibus. In istis
                        terre finibus totam istam petiam rectoribus ospitalis habeant teneant in
                        donicato tadiu quo isti predicti debitores solverint totum predictum debitum
                        XI librarum in manibus rectoris suprascripti ospitali post bladam recolta,
                        nisi sit cultata. Si tamen isti debitores mortui erunt priusquam debitum hoc
                        solutum sit totum, tunc terra ista de Pratale sit in proprio et in dominio
                        ospitalis. Sepiternaliter habeant, possideant expedite sine aliqua lite et
                        molestia alicuius heredis predictorum iugalium vel alicuius persone, sed
                        pacifice et quiete detineant. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: viginti librarum.
                        Actum in <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3227" key="#Castle">Gangalandi</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/83" key="#Comitatus">Florefti</geogName> (sic).
                        Signa manuum predictorum Passavanti et Berte, que legaliter notitia Benni
                        iudicis hanc cartulam fieri rogarunt. In presentia <persName
                            ref="#people/3227" key="#Witness">Uguicionis</persName> filius <persName
                            ref="#people/3228">Bonifatii</persName> et <persName ref="#people/3229"
                            key="#Witness">Paltonierii</persName> filius eius et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Widaloctus">Guidalotti</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainuccius de Gangalandi"
                                >Rinucini</name></persName> de Gangalandi et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hugolinus/Widuccius de ">Ugolini
                                Guiduci</name></persName> de Puzzo rogatorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs>. (S) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Judge"><name ref="Bennus"
                                >Benno</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> et <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, Signa
                        vocatus, interfui et ipsam Bertam interrogavi et hanc cartulam scripsi et
                        complevi.</ab>
                </div>
